    "description_long": "This is a compact, blue sports car with a boxy, retro-inspired design reminiscent of classic European city cars. The car features a white roof, black-tinted windows, and a pair of prominent round headlights at the front. Its body is streamlined with subtle fender flares and black trim outlining the wheel arches and windows. The wheels are dark alloy with a five-spoke pattern, and the tires are low-profile, suggesting a sporty intent. The rear of the car is simple, with a large rear window and a rectangular cutout for the license plate. The overall appearance is playful yet functional, suitable for urban environments.",
